In this interview Ian Lourens, CEO of OneLogix, shares his views on the opportunities and challenges of doing business in Africa, as well as his advice for other companies wanting to expand into the rest of the continent.This article is part of a series sponsored by Standard Bank Business Banking. Should you require further information about doing business in the rest of the continent please e-mail Moneyweb MD Marc Ashton with details of your project and he will connect you with an appropriate banking resource.